kkkanbun
================================================

Version: 1.0.5
Date: 2025-11-04
Author: Kosei Kawaguchi a.k.a. KKTeX
License: MIT

Description:
------------
This package, inspired by gckanbun, provides a comprehensive set of commands required for typesetting classical Chinese texts in Japanese style.

Munehiro Yamamoto, the author of the original package (: gckanbun package), generously granted permission to release this as kkkanbun package.

Dependencies:
-------------
luatex-ja (If you don't use jlreq class, you MUST load luatex-ja package in advance.)

